      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Notice of Punctuality Concern\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to our attention regarding your punctuality during your shifts. As you are aware, our company values punctuality and consistency, and it is essential for maintaining a productive work environment.\n\nOver the past two weeks, we have noticed that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts each day. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, it is crucial to address this issue promptly to ensure that it does not impact your performance or the overall workflow of our team.\n\nAs a first step towards resolving this matter, we kindly request that you make a concerted effort to arrive on time for your shifts moving forward. We believe that with your dedication and commitment, you will be able to meet this expectation.\n\nPlease understand that this is a formal warning, and we will be closely monitoring your punctuality. Should this issue persist, we may need to consider further disciplinary actions. We appreciate your cooperation and understanding in this matter.\n\nThank you for your attention to this important issue. We look forward to your prompt and positive response.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position",
      "source": "target",
