    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Immediate Attention Required: Punctuality Issue\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI trust this message finds you well. I am writing to address a pressing concern regarding your punctuality during your shifts. As you are aware, our company places a high value on punctuality and consistency, which are vital for maintaining a productive work environment.\n\nOver the past two weeks, we have observed that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts each day. While we understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, it is crucial to address this issue promptly to ensure that it does not impact your performance or the overall workflow of our team.\n\nYour tardiness not only affects your own productivity but also disrupts the established roster, causing inconvenience to your colleagues and potentially delaying the completion of tasks. We rely on each team member to adhere to the established roster to keep operations smooth and efficient.\n\nAs a first step towards resolving this matter, we kindly request that you make a concerted effort to arrive on time for your shifts moving forward. We believe that with your dedication and commitment, you will be able to meet this expectation.\n\nPlease understand that this is a formal warning, and we will be closely monitoring your punctuality. Should this issue persist,",
